{"tid":2192024,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"快必街站：投票選最想制裁的官員","createTime":"2020-09-07T00:19:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T00:20:29.000Z","uid":36494,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"93f09ac5f0a896a12045ccf6aa97f1b2df6c9c6d","tid":2192024,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T00:19:08.000Z","msg":"「快必」譚得志涉發表煽動文字被捕，翻查他於涉案6月至8月擺街站時的facebook影片，他曾舉辦健康講座，讓市民以貼紙投選最想制裁的官員，並向市民派發一包五個口罩，代表「五大訴求，缺一不可」，亦曾帶頭高呼「黑警死全家」，並呼叫「光復香港」後，在場有人和應「 時代革命」口號。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n快必上月初兩次健康講座直播中，擺出「最受歡迎（制裁）官員選舉」的宣傳紙板，印有11名被美國制裁的中港官員樣貌，讓市民投票。他曾提及會一直舉辦健康講座，「一直做到制裁晒所有政府高官、狗官，同埋制裁晒所有建制派藍絲立法會議員，同埋差佬。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n他7至8月也有在旺角等地抗議，警方多次到場查問，片段可見他有針對警方執法問題的言論，包括帶頭高呼「831打死人」、「黑警死全家」等，有市民和應，他指「嗌呢啲口號係我哋言論自由嘅範圍」。譚亦曾在街站批評政府拒封關，質疑全民檢疫目的。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200907/V6QDYLF3GVFWBBH44YSIC2QDF4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200907%2FV6QDYLF3GVFWBBH44YSIC2QDF4%2F&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNp5zZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=1d480919\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200907%2FV6QDYLF3GVFWBBH44YSIC2QDF4%2F&h=3a95217f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200907/V6QDYLF3GVFWBBH44YSIC2QDF4/</a>"},{"pid":"9eac7b161c3c7c6a9521c7bfd4c947cd2b429d5e","tid":2192024,"uid":36494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T00:19:56.000Z","msg":"好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85a22d4ab8c4e8cf4c577c1d22d0da7525a1a2d4","tid":2192024,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T00:20:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ff7857e6385e97386ca8648f2a562b57b48fcb14","tid":2192024,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T00:20:19.